npx create-react-app firstapp

Component
# Functional
> Dumb component
> Use for the purpose display only
> Cannot maintain the state

# ClassComponent
> Logical Componet
> Use to logics as well as display
> We can maintain the state


> Hooks

State
> State act like a local variable
> Every component can have its own state
> State are mutable (we can update the value)

Props
> Use to transfer the data between 2 nested component
> Value of props cannot updated